## Complete Request Lifecycle

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant Middleware
    participant ContextEngine
    participant Pipeline
    participant Database
    participant AI

    User->>Frontend: Type message
    
    Frontend->>Frontend: translate()
    Frontend->>Frontend: detectLanguage()
    
    Frontend->>API: POST /chatbot {message}
    
    API->>Middleware: authenticate(token)
    Middleware->>API: user authenticated
    
    API->>ContextEngine: assemble(params)
    
    ContextEngine->>Pipeline: assembleParallel(params)
    
    Note over Pipeline: Stage 0: Parallel fetch
    Pipeline->>Database: fetch settings
    Pipeline->>Database: embed message
    Pipeline->>Database: fetch conversation
    
    Note over Pipeline: Stage 1: Detection
    Pipeline->>Database: semantic search topics
    Pipeline->>Database: semantic search entities
    
    Note over Pipeline: Stage 2: Bundle compilation
    Pipeline->>Database: fetch identity bundle
    Pipeline->>Database: fetch preference bundle
    Pipeline->>Database: JIT retrieve memories
    Pipeline->>Database: fetch topic bundles
    
    Note over Pipeline: Stage 3: Assembly
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: calculate budget
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: compile system prompt
    
    Pipeline-->>ContextEngine: systemPrompt + metrics
    
    ContextEngine->>AI: generateResponse(prompt)
    
    Note over AI: Stream response back
    
    AI-->>ContextEngine: stream chunks
    ContextEngine-->>API: stream chunks
    
    API-->>Frontend: stream to UI
    
    Frontend->>User: Display response
    
    Note over Pipeline: Post-processing
    ContextEngine->>Database: extract ACUs
    ContextEngine->>Database: update memory graph
    ContextEngine->>Pipeline: invalidate cache
```

